@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = test-tenant

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### OIDC Discovery Document
GET {{baseUrl}}/.well-known/openid-configuration
Accept: application/json

###

### Token Introspection (invalid token - returns inactive)
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/introspect
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token=invalid-test-token&token_type_hint=access_token

###

### Token Revocation
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/revoke
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token=any-token-to-revoke

###

### Token Request - Authorization Code Grant (will fail without valid code)
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

grant_type=authorization_code&client_id=test-client&code=test-code&code_verifier=test-verifier-that-is-at-least-43-characters-long&redirect_uri=https://localhost/callback

###

### Token Request - Refresh Token Grant (will fail without valid refresh token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

grant_type=refresh_token&refresh_token=your-refresh-token-here&client_id=test-client

###

### Authorization Endpoint (initiates OAuth flow)
# Open this URL in a browser to start the authorization flow
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=test-client&redirect_uri=https://localhost/callback&scope=openid%20profile&state=random-state-value&code_challenge=test-challenge&code_challenge_method=S256
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

###

### User Info Endpoint (requires valid access token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/userinfo
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###
